\begin_layout Enumerate
三个点可以产生两条连线
\begin_inset Formula $P_{01}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $P_{12}$
\end_inset

。在
\begin_inset Formula $P_{01}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $P_{12}$
\end_inset

两条线上分别取两个点
\begin_inset Formula $Q_{0}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $Q_{1}$
\end_inset

，满足
\begin_inset Formula 
