\begin_inset Formula $Q_{01}$
\end_inset

，这条连线上又可以取一个点
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

，令
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

点同样是等比例点，即现在三个点的位置满足
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\abs*{P_{0}Q_{0}}}{\abs*{P_{0}P_{1}}}=\frac{\abs*{P_{1}Q_{1}}}{\abs*{P_{1}P_{2}}}=\frac{\abs*{Q_{0}R}}{\abs*{Q_{0}Q_{1}}}
\]

