\begin_layout Standard
均匀磁场
\begin_inset Formula $\sbf B$
\end_inset

中被加速的粒子，速度达到极限之后作匀速圆周运动。洛伦兹力公式结合相对论动力学：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
qc\sbf\beta\times\sbf B=\gamma mc\left[\gamma^{2}\sbf\beta\left(\sbf\beta\cdot\dot{\sbf\beta}\right)+\dot{\sbf\beta}\right]
\]

\end_inset

当
\begin_inset Formula $\sbf\beta\cdot\dot{\sbf\beta}=0$
\end_inset

时，
\begin_inset Formula $qc\sbf\beta\times\sbf B=\gamma mc\dot{\sbf\beta}$
\end_inset

。设
\begin_inset Formula $\left(\sbf\beta,\sbf B,\dot{\sbf\beta}\right)$
\end_inset

的方向成右手螺旋。
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
qc\beta B=\gamma mc\dot{\beta}\Rightarrow\dot{\beta}=\frac{q\beta B}{\gamma m}
\]

\end_inset

粒子的加速度为
\begin_inset Formula $\dot{\beta}=\frac{\beta^{2}}{R},$
\end_inset

所以
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
qc\beta B=\gamma mc\frac{\beta^{2}}{R}\Rightarrow\frac{qBR}{m}=\gamma\beta
\]

\end_inset

令
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha=\frac{qB}{m}$
\end_inset

，则
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\alpha^{2}R^{2}=\frac{\beta^{2}}{1-\beta^{2}},\quad\beta=\frac{R\alpha}{\sqrt{1+R^{2}\alpha^{2}}}
\]

\end_inset

辐射功率为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{q^{2}\dot{\beta}^{2}}{6\pi\varepsilon_{0}c}\gamma^{4}=\frac{q^{2}\gamma^{4}}{6\pi\varepsilon_{0}c}\frac{q^{2}\beta^{2}B^{2}}{\gamma^{2}m^{2}}=\frac{q^{2}\alpha^{2}}{6\pi\varepsilon_{0}c}\left(\gamma^{2}-1\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
粒子速度稳定时，辐射功率等于加速器提供的功率，即
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & \frac{q^{2}\alpha^{2}}{6\pi\varepsilon_{0}c}\left(\gamma^{2}-1\right)=qU\frac{c\beta}{2\pi R}\\
 & \frac{q\alpha^{2}}{3\varepsilon_{0}c^{2}}\left(\gamma^{2}-1\right)=U\frac{\beta}{R}=U\frac{qB}{\gamma m}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

代入
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{qBR}{m}=\gamma\beta$
\end_inset

，得到：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\gamma\left(\gamma^{2}-1\right)=3\frac{U}{q}\frac{\varepsilon_{0}c^{2}}{\alpha}=\frac{3U}{q\alpha\mu_{0}}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha=\frac{qB}{m}$
\end_inset

。由此式可确定
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma,\beta$
\end_inset

，进一步可确定
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
R=\frac{\gamma\beta}{\alpha}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

